# ValiChord — Screencast Script

**Runtime:** ~10 minutes
**Format:** Screen recording of terminal, no camera needed
**What to record:** Full terminal session from the `pkill` cleanup through to the final test summary
**Recommended tool:** OBS, QuickTime, or any screen recorder. Font size up to 16pt minimum.

---

## Before you hit record

Set up your terminal:
```bash
cd /workspaces/ValiChord/valichord
export PATH="/home/codespace/.cargo/bin:$PATH"
# Make the font large, clear the screen
```

Have the test command ready to paste, but don't run it yet.

